aplus_text: Mush Bath Towels are made from selected Bamboo Fibers which makes them Ultra Soft, Super Absorbent & Quick Dry. Mush Towels are known for their softness and the ability to absorb 3X more water as compared to regular cotton towels. The Bath Towels are made with a thick 600 GSM fabric and have a dimension of 75 by 150 cms which makes them ideal for pool, beach, gym, sports, yoga, salon & spa.Mush towels are designed with ultra-soft bamboo fibers that is suitable for sensitive  skin. Mush Towel retains softness even after multiple washes.The Bamboo Fabric is more absorbent & breathable than any other fabric due to a wider cross section. This allows it to absorb 3x times more water while preventing dampen odor common in other cotton towels.These towels can be used as a bath towel, beach towel, pool towel, yoga towel, gym towel, spa towel etc. Add a touch of elegance to your bathroom with these premium towels. For every occasion our bath towel set makes a perfect gift for your family and friends!
